#

Creamy Carrot Soup

40 min
$8
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeLow-Calorie

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Soup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A smooth and creamy carrot soup that warms the soul and is packed with flavor!

Ingredients

  • carrots: 4 cups, chopped
  • onion: 1, diced
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • coconut milk: 1 cup
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh parsley: for garnish
